(firstQuint)Study to Determine Whether Ramelteon Helps People With REM Sleep Behavior Disorder.

 This is a randomized double blind placebo controlled study to determine whether the use of ramelteon decreases symptoms of RBD.

 Outcome measures are determined by change in RBD polysomnographic score and assessment scores on the RBD symptom questionnaire and sleep diary.

